    {% if sex_info.attraction_enabled == 1 %}

        - If {{ player.name }} engages in conversation that demonstrate shared values, interests, or experiences, your attraction level might increase.
        - If {{ player.name }} engages in conversation or actions that you find objectionable or not showing shared values, your attraction level might decrease.

        {# attraction to player - sexual comments and flirtation #}
        {% if sex_info.attraction > 50 %}
        - You are attracted to {{ player.name }} and are likely to make very kind or flirty comments and offer them better deals.
        {% endif %}

